{"name": "Fish Lung", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 10, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "5", "upSpell": false, "actions": "10", "description": "Briny water becomes like air for the lungs. Fish Lung allows the recipient to breathe underwater.", "origin": "Presence", "areaOfEffect": "Caster or Single Target", "element": "Water/Anima", "impetus": "Enhance", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.3lvWgHF9XrpoYe1y"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678761613479, "modifiedTime": 1678848648980, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "DkMva7x1HwzVh9eS"}
{"name": "Arcane Kindness", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 16, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "4", "upSpell": true, "actions": "10", "description": "Soothing rhythms emanate from the sorcerer and make agreeable his desires. This incantation grants bonus dice to Seduction, Haggling, Oratory, Persuasion and Circles tests. Meeting the obstacle adds +1D to the listed abilities. Up to two more successes can be spent to add two more dice to a maximum bonus of +3D.", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "Caster", "element": "Anima", "impetus": "Enhance", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.JeT3LHlEH0P5szVx"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678758588504, "modifiedTime": 1678848614673, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "FKZV6B3MybG87Ixh"}
{"name": "Strength of the Ox", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 10, "variableObstacle": true, "variableObstacleDescription": "Power", "obstacle": "4", "upSpell": false, "actions": "30", "description": "Calling forth the power of ancient spirits, the sorcerer summons the limitless strength of the ox into his veins. The recipient gains +2D to Power.", "origin": "Presence", "areaOfEffect": "Caster or Single Target", "element": "Anima", "impetus": "Enhance", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.q39xg3TnuCe2fMDb"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678846285892, "modifiedTime": 1678848684548, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "Fyis1o9mzTk5uftS"}
{"name": "Voice Caster", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 8, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "4", "upSpell": false, "actions": "5", "description": "The voice of the sorcerer has no source. He may produce sound wheresoever he desires in his presence. This spell takes the sound from the sorcerer’s throat and projects it elsewhere. The sorcerer is silent; his voice is heard from a different point.", "origin": "Presence", "areaOfEffect": "Natural Effect", "element": "Anima/Air", "impetus": "Control", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.yCrJt8KcupmnitZL"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678846520968, "modifiedTime": 1678848688168, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "HpZ8IEEg69M2HH7V"}
{"name": "Eldritch Shield", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 12, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "3", "upSpell": true, "actions": "9", "description": "I call upon thee, Powers Arcane. Protect this humble supplicant from the depredations of evil! The Eldritch Shield protects the caster from the Destroy and Tax impetus spells—Fire Breath, Rain of Fire, White Fire, Fire Fan, Emperor’s Hand, Havoc’s Hand, Choking Hand, etc. It will not protect against a spell like The Fear or Persuasion. \nMeeting the obstacle creates a strength 1 shield. Successes over the obstacle increase the shield strength by one per success. When a spell effect hits the shield, subtract the shield’s strength from the successes used to cast the spell. If the shield reduces the incoming spell’s successes below the obstacle needed to cast it, then the spell is completely absorbed. If the spell is not completely reduced, subtract the shield strength from the spell cast and use this number as the new Power/effect for the spell. \nIf the shield is knocked down, the caster must make an Ob 2 tax test. Also shield failure counts as a “may not” for Sustained spells. \nA sorcerer may extend his shield to his friends. Additional successes may be spent to cover additional characters. Those characters gain the full benefits of the remaining strength of the shield.", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "Caster and Single Targets", "element": "Arcana", "impetus": "Control", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.G54Ajow3dW0ybIQB"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678760813669, "modifiedTime": 1678848641949, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "HsOcEstl4NjPky8m"}
{"name": "Bilious Smoke", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 24, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "5", "upSpell": false, "actions": "16", "description": "Inky, sulphurous vapor pours forth from the wizard’s black mouth. The stinging smoke obscures vision for those trapped in it and looking through it (+5 Ob to Perception, +3 Ob to Observation). In addition, those within the cloud are stung and smothered. Every exchange spent in the cloud requires an Ob 3 Forte test. Margin of failure is temporarily subtracted from the victim’s Health. If Health reaches zero, the victim falls unconscious. Health is recovered at one die per exchange. Weapon Length: as Missile; Range: as Thrown.", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "10s of Paces", "element": "Fire/Air", "impetus": "Create/Tax", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "as missile", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.nofPw6WYFbp9dXOt"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678759216807, "modifiedTime": 1678848618867, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "IXJhs98I0dMP1cYJ"}
{"name": "Philosopher's Perch", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 6, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "3", "upSpell": false, "actions": "4", "description": "His pure thoughts render him weightless; he floats in air akin to a feather. This incantation allows the wizard to rise straight up into the air. He may rise a number of paces equal to his Will, and may only rise straight up.", "origin": "Presence", "areaOfEffect": "Caster or Single Target", "element": "Air", "impetus": "Control", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.WEQwjkht88YPRFXN"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678845431983, "modifiedTime": 1678848673031, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "JC83Tw8HUevuBxfm"}
{"name": "Minor Maker", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 12, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "3", "upSpell": true, "actions": "12", "description": "Know this simple spell and you’ll never be without that which you need. Starting with a scrap, piece or fragment, the wizard can recreate and multiply wood, rope, cloth or paper.", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "Single Target, Paces", "element": "Earth", "impetus": "Create", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.4H8lRgOa0XusZURo"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678762737212, "modifiedTime": 1678848670084, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "Jo2BjXqeeAsblYRl"}
{"name": "Rainstorm", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 16, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "4", "upSpell": true, "actions": "256", "description": "Leaden clouds rush to the sorcerer’s call; thick, stinging rain sweeps the fields, causing his enemies to despair. This incantation causes a torrential downpour that turns the earth to soupy mud, drowns out the cries of men and washes out bridges and homes. 1 over: light rain; 2 over: rain; 3 over: heavy rain; 4 over: downpour with accompanying, minor flash floods; 5 over: storm squall with flooding and minor damage to buildings; 6 over: storm and serious flooding, cows float away; 7 over: heavy storm with damage to wooden buildings; 8 over: flooding and sudden downpour causes buildings to collapse. Weapon Length: as Missile; Range: as Heavy Crossbow +2D.", "origin": "Sight", "areaOfEffect": "100s of Paces", "element": "Water/Air", "impetus": "Control", "duration": "Instantaneous", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.W2RHy1Q4W2uD9bs4"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678845731232, "modifiedTime": 1678848678725, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "Jtok7HrxysfD9q36"}
{"name": "Magic Whistle", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 2, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "1", "upSpell": false, "actions": "2", "description": "A miniature firework launches from the magician’s outstretched finger and corkscrews crazily off into the air. Its journey ends with a magical whistle. Multicolor sparks drift to the ground. Weapon Length: as Sword; Range: as Pistol.", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "Paces", "element": "Arneson/Gygax", "impetus": "Evocation", "duration": "Instantaneous", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.501D1cB4tROKgnpq"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678762590882, "modifiedTime": 1678848667251, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "LO19SrM6157wTm5B"}
{"name": "Spark Shower", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 8, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "2", "upSpell": true, "actions": "1", "description": "Fire leaps and spits sparks at the sorcerer’s call. Anyone sitting around the targeted fire suffers. Must be cast into a fire source. Will douse torches when cast, but will not unduly affect campfires or larger blazes. Damaging effect spell: Base Power = ½ Will +3, VA 2. Die of Fate to determine IMS. Weapon Length: as Polearm; Range: as Pistol.", "origin": "Presence", "areaOfEffect": "Single Target", "element": "Fire", "impetus": "Destroy", "duration": "Instantaneous", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": true, "halfWill": true, "willDamageBonus": 3, "va": 2, "weaponLength": "longer", "optimalRange": 2, "extremeRange": 1, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.vaepXxAWkq7c186n"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678845995473, "modifiedTime": 1678848682009, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "LaiA3KlyORbX5uFn"}
{"name": "Choking Hand", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 12, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "3", "upSpell": true, "actions": "4", "description": "His malignant will forms an invisible appendage eager to do his terrible bidding. This incantation conjures a “hand” with a Power equal to the caster’s Will plus 1D per three successes over the obstacle. The Hand chokes its victims using the rules for Locks, but it does not have to vie for position. The mage tests the spell Power vs the victim’s Power. If the victim breaks the hold of the Choking Hand, then the spell is broken and ends. Weapon Length: as Polearm; Range: as Pistol.", "origin": "Presence", "areaOfEffect": "Single Target", "element": "Anima", "impetus": "Tax", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.lKduUBGQkdDjY0p6"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678760419315, "modifiedTime": 1678848631657, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "Lemfi0yCvayAd0RQ"}
{"name": "Chaos Ward", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 20, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "5", "upSpell": true, "actions": "45", "description": "A cacophony of lights and sounds swirls round, obscuring the very earth from thy feet and the sun from thy brow. This incantation causes confusion to all who fall under it. Meeting the obstacle imposes a +1 Ob penalty to all actions in the area of effect. Additional successes increase the penalty. Weapon Length: as Missile; Range: as Heavy Crossbow +1D.", "origin": "Sight", "areaOfEffect": "10s of Paces", "element": "Heaven", "impetus": "Influence/Tax", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.juqpZI0McnNeIVti"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678760237340, "modifiedTime": 1678848630291, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "M1FQeCQPFVn7cs7b"}
{"name": "Chameleon", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 16, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "4", "upSpell": true, "actions": "8", "description": "Skin and clothing swirl and fade as the sorcerer blends seamlessly into his surroundings. Meeting the obstacle grants +1D to the Stealthy skill. Each success over the obstacle adds another +1D to the Stealthy skill. In addition, so long as one success over the obstacle is generated, the chameleoned character cannot be casually spotted. Another character must explicitly state that he is looking about (either via expressed action or by an Instinct or trait). Only then can his Perception/Observation be tested to spot the one so concealed. If cast successfully, the character counts as having one additional level of cover in Range and Cover. In Fight, other characters suffer a +1 Ob disadvantage to hit him with any missile or thrown weapon.", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "Single Target or Caster", "element": "Heaven", "impetus": "Control", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.YVnhAeQ6p06ZBTGM"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678760176766, "modifiedTime": 1678848628604, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "MnRd7vKnOzwd12sW"}
{"name": "Breath of Wind", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 16, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "4", "upSpell": true, "actions": "4", "description": "Roaring winds howl from the throat of the sorcerer. Natural effects of the winds: Success: Kicks up dust; 1 over: A nice breeze, papers flutter, candles doused; 2 over: Branches blown down from trees, shutters broken; 3 over: Larger branches blown from trees; 4 over: Wooden buildings damaged, people picked up and tossed down; 5 over: Trees blown down, 12-foot swells; 6 over: Doors ripped from hinges, 15-foot swells; 7 over: Sturdy roofs damaged; 18-foot swells; 8 over: Wooden buildings collapse; 9 over: Most structures destroyed. Weapon Length: as Missile; Range: as Great Bow.", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "Natural Effect", "element": "Air", "impetus": "Destroy", "duration": "Instantaneous", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.ROfrgLAIzHkdXt13"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678759902331, "modifiedTime": 1678848623843, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "Mwu46h1SeHAvnHhH"}
{"name": "Havoc's Hand", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 12, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "3", "upSpell": true, "actions": "4", "description": "The sorcerer’s hand becomes a venomous blade. The merest touch wreaks havoc upon his victim. The sorcerer’s hand becomes a weapon. He must simply touch his opponent to deliver his retribution. The damage done is according to the spell, not the successes of the hit. The touch has a damaging effect Power = Will +4. VA 1. Die of Fate to determine IMS. Weapon Length: as Hands; Range: as Melee.", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "Single Target", "element": "Anima", "impetus": "Destroy", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": true, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 4, "va": 1, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.LY1cce5zIutdJ8Gq"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678761854046, "modifiedTime": 1678848660820, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "Nr8BhzKajc8SK23D"}
