{"name": "Dexterity of the Cat", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 12, "variableObstacle": true, "variableObstacleDescription": "1 + Speed", "obstacle": "4", "upSpell": false, "actions": "35", "description": "Purring incantations imbue the recipient with the infallible balance of the cat. +2D are added to the character’s Speed for purposes of climbing, leaping, dodging and other cat-like actions (including fighting, but not sprinting or long distance running).", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "Single Target or Caster", "element": "Anima", "impetus": "Enhance", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.yUqc0sII8sdAp3Ne"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678760648126, "modifiedTime": 1678848640479, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "qXKzjGst5LHVvNIP"}
{"name": "Mend", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 16, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "4", "upSpell": true, "actions": "27", "description": "Under the witch’s careful tending, the wear and tear of daily life disappears from cloth, wood and even metal. Meeting the obstacle repairs clothing and shoes; 1 success over mends tools, weapons or 1D of shield damage; 2 over mends 1D of armor; 3 over repairs stuff like gears or 2D of armor; 4 over repairs machines, like a mill, or large tools like a plowshare.", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "Single Target", "element": "Heaven", "impetus": "Control", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.TZxFpM4N85am64ul"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678762673378, "modifiedTime": 1678848669238, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "r8Qj18qF1gGFvTmu"}
{"name": "Magesense", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp", "system": {"pointCost": 16, "variableObstacle": false, "variableObstacleDescription": "", "obstacle": "4", "upSpell": true, "actions": "300", "description": "Magesense is a powerful spell that extends the sorcerer’s senses from the realm of the mundane into that of the arcane. When this spell is erected, the mage sees, hears and smells magic. When a spell is cast within or an active spell enters his Magesense area of effect, the mage may make a Perception test using the following obstacles: high powered magic (major miracles, Mjölnir, the Burning Wheel, Ob 10 spells, Strength 10 spirits etc.) are Ob 1 to detect; moderately powered magic (minor miracles, Ob 5 spells, a risen corpse, the Belt of Flying, Dragon Slaying Sword, Spirit Weapons, Strength 5 spirits), Ob 5; low powered magic (Jade Amulet, bless/curse, Ob 2 spells, Strength 2 spirits), Ob 8. If successful, he can pinpoint the location of the magical effect—he does not instantly know the nature of the magic. \nExtra successes of the spell must be divided between the area of effect and the sensitivity. Area of effect expands the range, but sensitivity adds +1D per success to Perception for the purpose of detecting magic. Magesense is one of the abilities that allows a sorcerer to use Aura Reading. Therefore, once magic is detected, Aura Reading may be used to determine the exact nature of the ability. \nLastly, while the Magesense is being sustained, the sorcerer’s Perception counts as Observation for detecting Stealthy and Inconspicuous characters, and the sorcerer suffers a +1 Ob penalty to all physical activities like fighting, running and jumping.", "origin": "Personal", "areaOfEffect": "10s of Paces", "element": "Anima/Arcana", "impetus": "Enhance", "duration": "Sustained", "rpCost": 0, "isWeapon": false, "halfWill": false, "willDamageBonus": 0, "va": 0, "weaponLength": "shortest", "optimalRange": 0, "extremeRange": 0, "maxRange": "10 Paces", "collapsed": false, "skillId": "", "inPracticals": false, "learningProgress": 0}, "effects": [], "flags": {"core": {"sourceId": "Item.nkOioK3lGy89gg2i"}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "burningwheel", "systemVersion": "1.3.5", "coreVersion": "10.291", "createdTime": 1678762435667, "modifiedTime": 1678848666246, "lastModifiedBy": "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz"}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "6AsWewF7ZIZOXaTz": 3}, "_id": "sKCRHmJ24nicQbBZ"}
